      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah \"fleeting\" is a nice way to put it but it feels more like being a joke. if we're just a momentary glitch in a void that doesn't care, then all this effort to survive, to build things, to keep going... it just feels like we're fighting a losing battle against entropy for no reason. why keep participating in something so fundamentally pointless?",
